    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-08-26T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-08-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="28"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d28">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName corresp="#p_RFD1" type="from"
                            >Roosevelt</persName> to Prime Minister <persName corresp="#p_CC2"
                            type="to">Churchill</persName>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d28fn1">Sent via the White House Map Room and the British
                        Admiralty Delegation at Washington. <persName corresp="#p_CC2"
                            >Churchill</persName> was in Canada at this time.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hyde Park</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-08-26">August 26,
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">From: The President</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">To: <gloss target="#t_ColonelWarden1">Colonel Warden</gloss>,
                    Personal and Secret</p>
                <p>Number 347. I hope you have seen Uncle <gloss target="#t_Joe1">Joe</gloss>’s new
                    message which is greatly improved in its tone. As you and he know, I am lost
                    until Monday<note n="2" xml:id="d28fn2">August 30, 1943.</note> and I would let
                    a few days go by till we answer him.</p>
                <p>However, my first feeling is that he has come around to our secondary meeting and
                    that it should be held very soon.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
